0張內（如果唔係張張印滿a4），利申試過印唔夠十張彩色就玩完。如果用唔係原廠墨會平啲，但有可能會傷printer噴頭，加快printer壽命<br />\n<br />\n而連續供墨系統嘅printer，個樣係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fY1aEu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfY1aEu7.jpg&h=fcc76e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以直接倒墨入部機<br />\n<br />\n墨水價錢大概係300百鬆啲有四色<br />\n容量係講緊黑色可以去到～150ml；彩色～70ml<br />\n係普通嘅好多好多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你已經有printer，可以上網揾下個型號有冇得改機，不過要接受唔係原廠嘅風險。google可以揾下連續供墨 printer改機，價錢預幾舊水左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wrxSQe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wrxSQe.jpg&h=03d26fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇printer又想入手嘅就直接買連續供墨printer，留意返價錢方面會貴過普通printer幾舊，但墨水cost長遠計一定平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申買左e字頭連續供墨printer，官方話一套可以印7500張黑白，6000張彩色，我就唔係好信個數字，不過用左幾日印左近百張彩色a4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個墨盒顯示用左1格(total4格)多少少(未計佢一開頭bump上噴頭果半格），算係咁啦，我買一千樓下行貨連一套原廠墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />印嘅quality唔算靚，家用機水平啦，不過睇到細字又顔色分明，我收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有能力就印多啲，痴嘅時候見到中學啲細路就再俾啲佢地，始終佢地自己去文具譜印要幾蚊張，又唔知會唔會遇到啲咩人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps我係打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"講春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜都唔識，一係你俾型號我買。一係收皮。"},{"pid":"8b18b7fca4cadcdbde7e33049a8675ebe97fc320","tid":1584461,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{