/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有能力就印多啲，痴嘅時候見到中學啲細路就再俾啲佢地，始終佢地自己去文具譜印要幾蚊張，又唔知會唔會遇到啲咩人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps我係打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"講春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜都唔識，一係你俾型號我買。一係收皮。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"文中講e字頭連續供墨 拉落啲有埋型號<br />\n睇多少少野有咁難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />性急唔得嘅"},{"pid":"944e54bf022d362eabb20b96b4e41a8267b07314","tid":1584461,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fc1b8d1b04362acd6e28e5e0f0045f0fc2fb4db","tid":1584461,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"支持，今個月都出左部brother嘅，質素的確係差少少，但無限印左兩疊A4紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f795de82200f17f103f5f17508b00216147b7c","tid":1584461,"uid":145466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"供墨系統一遇水會溶"},{"pid":"2d797927918a4fda6f402f66de30e7678f6cfeef","tid":1584461,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f795de82200f17f103f5f17508b00216147b7c","tid":1584461,"uid":145466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:42:41.000Z","msg":"供墨系統一遇水會溶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" c